text: Md. A. Khaleq is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Mymensingh-7. ==Career== Khaleq was elected to parliament from Mymensingh-7 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Md. A. Khaleq
